301
00:17:08.637 --> 00:17:10.537
So what?

302
00:17:10.537 --> 00:17:13.937
So, you schemed what you did this time.

303
00:17:13.937 --> 00:17:15.737
Mr. Komatsu.

304
00:17:15.737 --> 00:17:17.837
It was Mr. Yukigaya.

305
00:17:17.837 --> 00:17:21.737
He was the one who wrote that love letter

306
00:17:21.737 --> 00:17:24.437
as well as pushed Mr. Fukurokoji down from here.

307
00:17:24.437 --> 00:17:26.337
What?

308
00:17:26.337 --> 00:17:30.337
You feigned being a woman and sent that letter out.

309
00:17:30.337 --> 00:17:32.937
Then you took Mr. Fukurokoji

310
00:17:32.937 --> 00:17:35.137
