383
00:21:36.437 --> 00:21:40.437
To think that I left evidence on a trash like that...

384
00:21:42.937 --> 00:21:45.537
Even if that were to be my hair,

385
00:21:45.537 --> 00:21:49.537
I have a million other ways to get away with it.

386
00:21:49.537 --> 00:21:53.537
But I'd never do something as unsightly as that.

387
00:21:53.537 --> 00:21:55.837
Because it wouldn't be me

388
00:21:55.837 --> 00:21:58.137
